===message:I agree with your comment that we have fancy lives today, but I think that if we didn't have all the technological advances it would surprise you what people can actually do.  I was watching this television show where people choose to try to lives their lives as it was done years ago.  From having no electricity, to no phone, to havings to grow their own food and finding was to earn money when they needed to purchase the things they were unable to create.  If was kind of interesting because this one family started making moonshine, needless to say that the ended up surving better than the other families.  The other families put down this family basically saying they cheated by breaking the law, but it wasn't a game to be won or lost.  It was and experience to be lived.  If we had to go back to the simplier life I think people's abilities would surprise you.
